I12(C) at least one readily accessible immersion suit for each individual on board that vessel when operating on the waters described in section 3102 of this title;

I12(D) marine radio communications equipment sufficient to effectively communicate with land-based search and rescue facilities;

I12(E) navigation equipment, including compasses, nautical charts, and publications;

I12(F) first aid equipment and medical supplies sufficient for the size and area of operation of the vessel; and

I12(G) ground tackle sufficient for the vessel.

