I12(1) temporarily relieve the master or individual in charge;

I12(2) temporarily take command of the vessel;

I12(3) in the case of a vessel required to have a log under chapter 113 of this title, immediately enter the details of the incident in the log; and

I12(4) report those details to the Secretary_

I13(A) by the most expeditious means available; and

I13(B) in written form transmitted within 12 hours after the vessel arrives at its next port.

