I89. General eligibility requirements

I11(a) T4In GeneralK._Except as otherwise provided, a certificate of documentation for a vessel may be issued under this chapter only if the vessel is_

I12(1) wholly owned by one or more individuals or entities described in subsection (b);

I12(2) at least 5 net tons as measured under part J of this subtitle; and

I12(3) not documented under the laws of a foreign country.

