I11(b) T4Eligible OwnersK._For purposes of subsection (a)(1), the following are eligible owners:

I12(1) An individual who is a citizen of the United States.

I12(2) An association, trust, joint venture, or other entity if_

I13(A) each of its members is a citizen of the United States; and

I13(B) it is capable of holding title to a vessel under the laws of the United States or a State.

Q04

I12(3) A partnership if_

I13(A) each general partner is a citizen of the United States; and

I13(B) the controlling interest in the partnership is owned by citizens of the United States.

