I13(A) it is incorporated under the laws of the United States or a State;

I13(B) its chief executive officer, by whatever title, and the chairman of its board of directors are citizens of the United States; and

I13(C) no more of its directors are noncitizens than a minority of the number necessary to constitute a quorum.

