I12(2) ownership and operation of the fleet by citizens of the United States insofar as practicable;

I12(3) vessels designed to afford the best and most complete protection for passengers and crew against fire and all marine perils; and

I12(4) an efficient capacity for building and repairing vessels in the United States with an adequate number of skilled personnel to provide an adequate mobilization base.

