I22``(2) T4Treatment as contractorK._For purposes of the application, under paragraph (1), of section 53107 of title 46, United States Code, to a vessel constructed with assistance under this subtitle, the term `contractor' as used in that section means the person who will be the operator of a vessel constructed with assistance under this subtitle.

