I89. Short sea transportation defined

I11In this chapter, the term ``short sea transportation'' means the carriage by a documented vessel of cargo_

I12(1) that is_

I13(A) contained in intermodal cargo containers and loaded by crane on the vessel; or

I13(B) loaded on the vessel by means of wheeled technology; and

