I89. Types of adjustments and arrangements

I11(a) T4Suspension RequirementsK._An adjustment or arrangement under this chapter shall include suspension of_

I12(1) the requirement to operate the vessel in foreign trade under the applicable operating-differential or construction-differential subsidy contract or mortgage or other agreement; and

